		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Credit risk</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Credit risk</b> is the risk of loss due to a debtor's non-payment of a <a href="/wiki/Loan" title="Loan">loan</a> or other line of credit (either the principal or <a href="/wiki/Interest" title="Interest">interest</a> (coupon) or both)</p>
